cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CE

The paper discusses the control of complex physical systems using machine learning techniques, specifically deep learning and model predictive control. This falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of recurrent neural networks (RNNs) for prediction and online learning also suggests the paper could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the application of these techniques to fluid flow control suggests the paper could also be categorized under computational engineering (cs.CE).
